description: PIMS 2439 BD2 FSP: CONSERVATION AND SUSTAINABLE USE OF BIODIVERSITY IN THE DALMATIAN COAST THROUGH GREENING COASTAL DEVELOPMENT

subproject.description:
Conservation and sustainable use of biodiversity in the Dalmatian coast through greening coastal development
Outcome 1: Biodiversity-friendly development is demonstrated in four small, globally important, productive landscapes.
Outcome 2: An improved investment climate for BD-friendly enterprises across the four counties.
Outcome 3:
Compliance with biodiversity-related regulations has increased significantly across all sectors across the four counties.
Outcome 4:  A national-level enabling environment that appreciates, supports, institutionalises and disseminates biodiversity-friendly development in coastal areas
